    "sourceCategory": "Tennis",
    "description": "Asics GEL-RESOLUTION X Clay W White/Pink SS26 Shoes - Stability, comfort and total control to dominate from the baseline. The Asics GEL-RESOLUTION X Clay W White/Pink SS26 have been designed for women players seeking a high-performance shoe capable of offering maximum stability, advanced cushioning and a great sense of security in every movement.. This model is especially aimed at players who play from the baseline and need solid and stable footwear to respond confidently in intense rallies, quick lateral movements and aggressive footwork during the match.. For this reason, the Asics Gel-Resolution X Clay incorporate technologies such as Dynawall which enhances stability, Dynalacing technology that helps create a secure fit during dynamic movements, and GEL technology in the forefoot. which improves shock absorption and promotes a smoother step.. Regarding design, they have been made in white and pink colours that provide a modern, elegant and feminine aesthetic, mixing a green colour on the sole that adds vibrant energy in a clean and sophisticated result.. Technical Features of the Asics GEL-RESOLUTION X Clay W White/Pink SS26. The Asics GEL-RESOLUTION X Clay W integrate specific technologies to improve lateral stability, shock absorption and durability in high-intensity matches on clay courts.. Brand: Asics. Model: Gel-Resolution X Clays. Season: SS26. Colour: White and pink with green details. Sole type: Espiga / Clay. Playing level: Intermediate / Advanced. Playing style: Control / Baseline. Technologies and materials of the Asics GEL-RESOLUTION X Clay W SS26. FF BLAST™ PLUS ECO: Soft cushioning and prolonged comfort. The midsole incorporates FF BLAST™ PLUS ECO technology, a lightweight and responsive foam designed to provide more comfortable and efficient cushioning throughout the match. This system improves shock absorption on intense footwork and helps reduce muscle fatigue, offering a constant feeling of comfort even in long and demanding matches.. DYNAWALL™: Greater stability in lateral movements. DYNAWALL™ technology has been developed to offer superior stability in lateral movements and quick changes of direction. In this new version, the structure extends to the heel area to provide firmer and more efficient support during aggressive footwork, helping to quickly recover position from the baseline.. DYNALACING™: Secure fit for dynamic movements. The DYNALACING™ system keeps the foot perfectly held during the most intense actions of the match. This technology improves the feeling of stability in accelerations, stops and quick transitions, preventing unnecessary foot movement inside the shoe and increasing security in every step.. GEL™ technology in the forefoot: Smoother and more stable steps. The incorporation of GEL™ technology in the forefoot area significantly improves shock absorption during jumps, landings and quick footwork. Thanks to this, players enjoy smoother transitions and a greater feeling of comfort in explosive movements and constant lateral displacements.. Two-piece midsole: Greater control and stability on footwork. The Asics GEL-RESOLUTION X Clay W feature a two-piece midsole design that promotes more stable and balanced landings. This construction helps improve control during intense footwork and increases security in aggressive lateral movements typical of baseline play.. AHARPLUS™ sole and PGUARD™ reinforcement: Enhanced durability for intensive play. The AHARPLUS™ rubber sole provides high wear resistance and excellent performance on clay courts. Additionally, PGUARD™ technology reinforces the inner forefoot area to protect the zones most exposed to abrasion caused by frequent dragging and braking.. More sustainable manufacturing: Lower environmental impact. The insole of the Asics GEL-RESOLUTION X Clay W has been manufactured using a solution-dyeing process that significantly reduces water consumption and carbon emissions compared to conventional methods. This system allows more responsible production without compromising the footwear's quality, comfort or performance.. Who are the Asics GEL-RESOLUTION X Clay W White/Pink SS26 for?. Baseline players seeking stability and control in every movement.. Intensive players who need durable and resistant footwear for training and competition.. Players with a defensive style who play from the baseline and look for comfortable and secure cushioning during long matches.. Intermediate and advanced level players who perform constant changes of direction and lateral footwork.. Conclusion: Control the pace of the match with stability and comfort with the Asics GEL-RESOLUTION X Clay W SS26. The Asics GEL-RESOLUTION X Clay W White/Pink SS26 combine advanced stability, efficient cushioning and support technologies designed to offer solid and secure performance from the baseline.. Thanks to systems like DYNAWALL™, DYNALACING™, FF BLAST™ PLUS ECO cushioning and GEL™ technology, these shoes allow you to move with greater confidence, better absorb impacts and maintain control in every point.. If you are looking for shoes that combine stability, durability, comfort and lateral security, the Asics GEL-RESOLUTION X Clay W SS26 are an excellent choice to take your performance to the next level.",
