    "source": "padel-market",
    "sourceProductId": "45115219566",
    "sourceCategory": "Tennis",
    "description": "Adidas RX Series Light 2024 Padel Racket - Absolute Control with additional stability for precise shots. This new Adidas RX Series Light padel racket&nbsp;redefines control and precision on the court. Designed with a round shape and a centered sweet spot that offers total control. This Adidas racket is ideal for players&nbsp;at an intermediate level who are looking for a control racket with a softer and more comfortable feel than other rackets in the Adidas range, as well as those who value a lightweight racket (345-360 gr) for greater maneuverability and faster changes of play.. In terms of its features, it has a cutting-edge design, a Fiber Glass surface that provides a more elastic and comfortable feel to return balls with greater comfort, and a core with EVA rubber Soft Performance, a low-density rubber that provides a more comfortable impact and a&nbsp;smooth ball output.&nbsp;. Without a doubt, the&nbsp;Adidas RX Series Light is a racket&nbsp;with high performance designed for players at an intermediate level who seek greater control in their shots while delivering precision and stability.&nbsp;. Technical Features of the Adidas RX Series Light 2024. The Adidas RX Series Light 2024 has been designed for players who prioritize&nbsp;control and defensive strategy and are looking for a racket that delivers precise and stable shots thanks to its Adidas technologies. The racket stands out for its round shape with a centered sweet spot and low balance&nbsp;which makes it easier to connect with the ball. Below are its technical specifications. Brand: Adidas. Model: RX Series Light. Year: 2024. Shape: Round. Balance: Low. Weight: 345-360 gr.. Core: Eva Soft Performance. Faces: Fiber Glass. Surface: Rough. Game Level: Intermediate. Game Type: Control. Advanced Features and Technologies of the Adidas RX Series Light 2024. Structural Power and Structural Reinforcement Technologies: Greater Rigidity and Power. One of the standout technologies in the Adidas RX Series Light is Structural Power. It is a design featuring a carbon fiber insert in the bridge of the racket that provides greater structural rigidity, thus increasing more powerful shots.. On the other hand, Structural Reinforcement stands out, consisting of perimeter reinforcements throughout the racket that allow greater resistance to the high torsions the racket withstands. In summary, with these two technologies you will not have to worry about either the durability of the racket or the hitting performance, as they provide the necessary rigidity against the torsions generated during impact.. Smart Holes Lineal: Greater durability of the racket. The Adidas RX Series Light incorporates Smart Holes Lineal technology. This is the arrangement of the holes of the racket equidistantly in groups of 3 which strengthens the surface improving the durability of the racket.. EVA Soft Performance and Fiber Glass: Comfortable Core without Sacrificing Firmness and Soft Feel with excellent ball output. The core of the RX Series Light 2024 incorporates EVA Soft Performance rubber. It is a rubber that offers a softer and more comfortable feel without sacrificing good ball output, making it perfect for players who seek controlled and precise shots in every point.. On the other hand, one of the advantages of EVA Soft Performance is that it provides a comfortable and controlled hitting sensation, helps absorb vibrations thanks to its softer feel and delivers great comfort, offering a perfect balance between comfort and firmness.&nbsp;. The surface of the Adidas RX Series Light is made of Fiber Glass, a highly flexible material that provides a comfortable feel and great ball output. This material&nbsp;on the faces offers a more elastic and comfortable touch, providing greater ball output and control in defensive shots and fast transitions.&nbsp;. Round Shape and Medium Sweet Spot: Maximum Control in defensive play. The round shape of the Adidas RX Series Light 2024 provides a medium sweet spot that maximizes control&nbsp;in every shot, making it perfect for defensive players who play with a defensive strategy. The round shape combined with a medium balance (weight in the center of the racket) makes this racket the ultimate defensive tool.. The round shape and technologies focused on reinforcing the structure of the racket and offering great precision make it an ideal option for those who enjoy a defensive game and master control, allowing them to execute clean and precise shots that pressure the opponent with patience.. Who Is This Adidas RX Series Light 2024 Padel Racket For?. The Adidas RX Series Light 2024 is the perfect choice for:. Players who&nbsp;compete or train frequently and play with a defensive strategy.. Intermediate players who seek rigid control without torsion in the racket without giving up solid ball output.. Players who want to dominate every point from the back of the court with a precise response.. Intermediate players or those starting in padel&nbsp;who want a control racket to improve their technique and move to the next level. Players who value a lighter racket to gain maneuverability and speed in changes of pace.. Frequently Asked Questions about the Adidas RX Series Light 2024. Is the Adidas RX Series Light 2024 suitable for beginners?. Although it is mainly designed for intermediate players, the Adidas RX Series Light 2024 can also be an excellent option for advanced beginners who are looking for a racket with absolute control and exceptional comfort. Its round shape and medium balance along with its reduced weight make it easier to learn technique, while the fiber glass provides a soft feel that forgives hitting errors.. What is the difference between the Adidas RX Series 2024 and the Adidas RX Series Light racket?. The main difference lies in the weight and maneuverability. The RX Series has a weight of 360-375 grams, while the RX Series Light is lighter (345-360 gr) offering greater agility and faster reaction speed. In short, the Light version is optimized for players who seek greater maneuverability and faster movements.. How is the ball output of this racket?. The ball output of the Adidas RX Series Light 2024 is excellent. Thanks to the combination of EVA Soft Performance rubber and Fiber glass, it enhances natural ball output from any area of the court, while the EVA Soft Performance core offers high elasticity that propels the ball with controlled power. In short, both features provide a surprising ball output.. Conclusion: The Adidas RX Series Light 2024 is the ideal racket for intermediate players seeking control and stability. The RX Series Light2024 is not just a control racket: it is a precision tool that allows you to dominate the game from a slow and defensive strategy, with an extra level of stability thanks to its technologies that improve the rigidity and structure of the racket. In addition, with its reduced weight, it will help intermediate players take their game to the next level.. With high-quality materials such as its Fiber Glass surface and EVA Soft Performance rubber core, and technologies specifically designed to unleash controlled and precise shots such as Structural Power, Structural Reinforcement or Smart Holes Curve , it guarantees exceptional performance in every point, allowing you to focus on executing control shots with total confidence and maneuverability. If you are looking for a&nbsp;padel racket that offers total control, absolute precision and a lightweight feel, the&nbsp;Adidas RX Series Light 2024 is your best option. If you want to level up, discover the Adidas RX Series Light 2024 and elevate your playing experience enjoying total control and precise shots with superior handling thanks to its lightweight design!",
