    "sourceCategory": "Tennis",
    "description": "Wilson Blade LS V4 Padel Green 2026 Racket - Lightness, control and versatility for intermediate players who want to evolve their game. The new Wilson Blade LS V4 Padel Green 2026 is a padel racket designed for intermediate-level players looking for a versatile tool capable of offering an excellent balance between control, power and comfort in every shot. In this case, the Wilson Blade LS has been specially designed for players who want a lightweight racket to gain manoeuvrability, smoother movements and reduced fatigue during play.. Thanks to its teardrop shape, medium balance and weight of just 355 grams, the Wilson Blade LS V4 Padel Green 2026 is the lightest racket in the Blade range, offering an ideal combination for those who want to continue progressing in their game. Its reduced weight provides faster reactions and smoother movements, allowing players to maintain a high level of performance for longer. In addition, its balanced behaviour allows precise defence from the back of the court while generating the power needed to dominate at the net.. This racket incorporates high-performance technologies such as its Fiberglass Weave faces, Soft EVA core, carbon tubular frame, Duo Grid Hole Pattern system and a rough surface among other advanced technologies that we will look at below for improved performance on court.. Its attractive design in a turquoise green shade combined with white details on the handle and faces provides a modern, fresh and sporty aesthetic that perfectly reflects the dynamic and versatile character of this racket.. Technical Features of the Wilson Blade LS V4 Padel Green 2026 Racket. The Wilson Blade LS V4 Padel Green racket stands out for its teardrop shape and medium balance, making it the ideal option for an all-round and versatile game, combining the power of diamond-shaped rackets with the control of round ones. On the other hand, it stands out for its weight of 355 g, a lightweight construction that improves movement speed, enhances manoeuvrability and reduces fatigue during long matches. Let's take a closer look at its features:. Brand: Wilson. Model: Blade LS V4 Padel Green. Year: 2026. Shape: Teardrop. Balance: Medium. Weight: 355 grams. Core: Soft EVA. Faces: Fiberglass Weave. Surface: Rough. Player Level: Intermediate. Game Type: All-round. Technologies and Materials of the Wilson Blade LS V4 Padel Green 2026 Racket. Fiberglass Weave: Greater comfort, ball output and ease of play. The faces of the Wilson Blade LS V4 Padel Green 2026 are made with Fiberglass Weave, a mesh of interwoven fibreglass threads that forms the outer layer of the racket. This material creates a flexible and elastic surface capable of generating excellent ball output with less effort.. Being more flexible than carbon, fibreglass acts like a spring effect, propelling the ball with ease and requiring less effort. On the other hand, it provides a more comfortable feel, absorbing part of the vibrations generated during impact and offering more pleasant sensations.. Soft EVA Core: Comfort, shock absorption and controlled power. The core of the Wilson Blade LS V4 Padel Green 2026 incorporates Soft EVA technology, a low-density foam developed to offer a comfortable and cushioned hitting feel. Thanks to its ability to absorb impacts, this foam reduces vibrations transmitted to the arm and provides superior comfort during play.. In addition, it has the firmness required to generate highly efficient ball output and the power needed to execute deep and consistent shots without having to apply great force on every hit. This combination makes Soft EVA an excellent ally for versatile and comfortable play.. C2 Tubular Frame: Carbon frame for maximum stability and durability. The C2 Tubular Construction technology consists of a carbon tubular construction manufactured with great precision to guarantee uniform thickness throughout the racket structure. This system significantly improves durability and impact resistance, preventing the twisting that occurs during hitting. Thanks to this, the racket transmits better sensations to the player, offering a cleaner and more precise response even on the most demanding shots.. Duo Grid Hole Pattern: Optimised power and control in every area of the racket. The Wilson Blade LS V4 Padel Green 2026 incorporates the innovative Duo Grid Hole Pattern drilling pattern, designed to optimise the racket's behaviour in different areas of the surface. The larger holes located in the upper section promote power generation in smashes, bandejas and overhead shots.. On the other hand, the smaller lower holes improve control, precision and the ability to generate spin on volleys and defensive shots. This distribution allows players to enjoy a more balanced and effective racket in any game situation.. Spin Texture: Rough surface to maximise spin. Another technology integrated into the Wilson Blade LS V4 Padel Green is Spin Texture technology, which incorporates a rough and textured finish on the racket faces to significantly improve ball grip during impact.. This increase in friction allows players to generate more pronounced spin with greater ease, providing greater control over the ball's trajectory and adding a tactical advantage over opponents. In addition, it provides a more precise and pleasant contact sensation that improves player confidence on every shot.. Who is the Wilson Blade LS V4 Padel Green 2026 for?. Intermediate players looking for a higher-performance racket to continue evolving technically.. All-round players who want a balance between power and control to adapt to any match situation.. Players looking for a greater ability to generate spin thanks to an advanced rough surface.. Players who base their strategy on the combination of offensive and defensive play and are constantly changing pace, needing a fast and comfortable racket that accompanies them in both styles of play.. Players who value lightweight rackets to reduce fatigue during matches and gain faster and smoother movements.. In short, the Wilson Blade LS V4 Padel Green 2026 is designed for those players who already have experience in padel and want a more advanced racket that allows them to improve their performance, refine their technique and compete with greater guarantees both in defence and attack, with superior lightness for faster and smoother movements.. Conclusion: The Wilson Blade LS V4 Padel Green 2026 is the perfect companion to evolve with greater lightness and comfort. The Wilson Blade LS V4 Padel Green 2026 combines control, power, manoeuvrability and comfort in a racket designed to help intermediate players continue growing on court.. Thanks to advanced technologies such as Fiberglass Weave, Soft EVA, C2 Tubular Construction, Duo Grid Hole Pattern or Spin Texture, this racket offers balanced performance that allows players to face any game situation with confidence and security.. If you are looking for a versatile, lightweight racket ready to accompany you in your sporting progression, the Wilson Blade LS V4 Padel Green 2026 is one of the best options to continue evolving and enjoy superior performance on every point, while also benefiting from greater comfort and faster movements thanks to its reduced weight.",
