    "sourceCategory": "Tennis",
    "description": "Wilson Rush Pro Ace Navy Blazer FW25 Shoes - Maximum comfort, wide fit and advanced stability to dominate the court. The Wilson Rush Pro Ace Navy Blazer FW25 have been designed for players seeking the perfect combination of comfort, stability, cushioning and support during the most intense matches.. This model stands out especially for incorporating a more generous fit and a wider toe box, making it an excellent choice for players with wide feet who need more space and comfort without sacrificing performance on the court.. Thanks to its technical construction and optimized cushioning from heel to toe, these shoes offer a more comfortable, stable and smooth step with every movement. Their navy blue design with white and red details provides an elegant, sporty and modern aesthetic, ideal for players who seek performance and style in every match.. Technical Features of the Wilson Rush Pro Ace Navy Blazer FW25 Padel Shoes. The Wilson Rush Pro Ace FW25 incorporate advanced technologies developed to maximize stability, comfort and structural support during play. Thanks to their 2E fit for wider feet and their combination of reactive cushioning and lateral stability, they offer a much safer and more comfortable playing experience.. Brand: Wilson. Model: Rush Pro Ace. Season: FW25. Color: Navy blue with white and red details. Sole type: All Court / Mixta. Playing level: Intermediate / Advanced. Designed for: Maximum comfort, stability and wide fit. Fit: 2E last for wide feet. Technologies and Materials of the Wilson Rush Pro Ace Navy Blazer FW25. 2E Last and Wide Toe Box: Greater comfort for wide feet. One of the most distinctive aspects of the Wilson Rush Pro Ace is its 2E fit construction, specially designed for players with wider feet who need a greater sense of space and comfort inside the footwear.. The wider toe box allows a more natural adaptation of the foot, reducing pressure points and improving comfort during long matches or intensive training sessions.. 4D Support Chassis: Superior stability and enhanced movement control. The 4D Support Chassis technology incorporates an asymmetrical chassis from heel to toe designed to improve stability and control pivot movements. This system helps limit supination and provides greater security during quick direction changes and aggressive lateral movements, allowing you to play with more confidence and control on every point.. DF2 and R-DST+: Reactive cushioning and continuous comfort. The Wilson Rush Pro Ace FW25 feature a combination of DF2 technology and reactive R-DST+ foam, designed to offer excellent impact absorption and a smoother transition from heel to toe.. The 9 mm drop provides the perfect balance between comfort and performance, while the midsole foam enhances cushioning and energy return to promote a more dynamic and comfortable stride.. Sensifeel: Lightness, ventilation and comfortable fit. The upper construction incorporates Sensifeel technology, made up of minimal layers of material that improve breathability and reduce the weight of the footwear.. Thanks to this lightweight and flexible structure, the shoes offer a greater sense of comfort and ventilation without losing support or stability during play.. OrthoLite EVA Molded: Durable cushioning and maximum comfort. The high-density OrthoLite EVA Molded insole provides soft and durable padding that significantly improves comfort during play.. This technology helps reduce fatigue and maintains excellent cushioning capacity even after intensive use, offering a more comfortable feeling on every step.. Duralast and Medial Rubber Drag Pad: Durability and reinforced protection. The Wilson Rush Pro Ace incorporate the Duralast compound, a high-density rubber designed to offer maximum abrasion resistance and excellent traction on different surfaces.. Additionally, the Medial Rubber Drag Pad system adds extra protection on the medial side of the foot, increasing the durability of the footwear against wear caused by drags and aggressive movements.. Who are the Wilson Rush Pro Ace Navy Blazer FW25 Shoes for?. Players with wide feet who need a more comfortable and spacious fit.. Intermediate and advanced players seeking stability and lateral support.. Athletes who prioritize comfortable and soft cushioning during long matches.. Players who perform intense lateral movements and frequent direction changes.. Players looking for a durable, stable and comfortable shoe for frequent use.. Conclusion: Comfort, stability and wide fit with the Wilson Rush Pro Ace Navy Blazer FW25. The Wilson Rush Pro Ace Navy Blazer FW25 have been developed to offer an outstanding balance between comfort, stability and durability in the most demanding padel.. Thanks to technologies such as 4D Support Chassis, DF2, R-DST+, Sensifeel and the OrthoLite EVA Molded insole, these shoes provide a great sense of security, cushioning and comfort throughout the entire match.. If you are looking for shoes that combine wide fit, lateral stability, reactive cushioning and maximum comfort, the Wilson Rush Pro Ace Navy Blazer FW25 are an excellent choice to perform at your best on the court.",
