    "description": "Adidas MULTIGAME Tonal Black 2026 Backpack - Versatile organization, reinforced durability, and practical design for everyday use. The Adidas Multigame Tonal Black 2026 backpack is designed for players seeking a practical, durable, and well-organized solution to carry their equipment both during training and daily routines. This model stands out for its all-black design, offering an elegant, discreet, and professional look on and off the court.. Focusing on versatility of use, this backpack combines capacity, comfort, and smart solutions such as its main roll-top opening, which allows adjusting the volume between 42 and 48 litres depending on your needs and the load you want to carry. Additionally, it includes a specific compartment with capacity for one racket featuring thermal protection and a semi-rigid structure, ensuring superior protection against impacts and temperature changes.. Made with high-quality technical materials, this backpack guarantees excellent wear resistance and moisture protection, making it an ideal choice for players who want functionality without sacrificing style.. Technical Features of the Adidas Multigame Tonal Black 2026 Backpack. The Adidas Multigame Tonal Black 2026 stands out for its versatile organization and design optimized for daily use, offering multiple access points and compartments to keep all your equipment orderly. Let's look at its features in detail:. Brand: Adidas. Model: Multigame Tonal Black. Season: 2026. Bag Type: Backpack. Colour: Black. Capacity: 42-48L adjustable thanks to the roll-top system. Dimensions: 29 x 15.5 x 47 cm. Materials: 100% recycled 900D polyester with TPU coating + 100% recycled 210D polyester + Raincover. Compartments: Main compartment with roll-top opening, semi-rigid thermal compartment for one racket, front zip pocket, left elastic mesh side pocket, and right zip side pocket. Design: Reinforced TPE base, padded back panel, and ergonomic structure for daily use. Technologies and Materials of the Adidas Multigame Tonal Black 2026 Backpack. Roll-top system: Adjustable capacity and enhanced protection. One of the key elements of this backpack is its main roll-top opening, a system that allows rolling the top part to adjust capacity according to the load volume. This design not only provides versatility but also improves protection against moisture or dirt ingress.. It also features buckle closures and an additional zipper, ensuring greater security and preventing accidental openings during transport.. Semi-rigid thermal racket compartment: Advanced protection. The backpack includes an external semi-rigid compartment with thermal insulation, designed so the racket fits perfectly and is protected from impacts and temperature changes.. This structure helps keep the racket in optimal conditions, avoiding deformations or performance loss caused by external factors, a feature highly valued by demanding players.. 900D recycled polyester with TPU coating: Durability and resistance. Made with 900D recycled polyester, this backpack offers great resistance to wear, abrasion, and intensive use. The TPU coating adds an extra layer of protection against moisture and splashes, enhancing product durability.. The interior of 210D recycled polyester maintains lightness without compromising resistance, while the raincover provides additional protection in rainy conditions.. Reinforced TPE base: Greater resistance to intensive use. The base of the backpack incorporates a TPE reinforcement, a durable material that protects the structure against wear caused by contact with hard or wet surfaces, increasing the backpack's lifespan and providing extra protection for your equipment.. Practical organization with multiple access points. The Adidas Multigame Tonal Black design includes a front zip pocket for quick access to personal items, a left elastic mesh side pocket ideal for bottles, and a right zip side pocket for more secure accessories.. This layout facilitates efficient organization and quick access to essentials at any time.. Padded back panel: Comfort on every move. The padded back panel enhances comfort during transport, adapting to the back and reducing pressure while moving. This feature is key for comfortable and prolonged daily use.. Who is the Adidas Multigame Tonal Black 2026 Backpack for?. Players looking for a versatile backpack for everyday use.. Regular players who need to carry their equipment in an organized way.. Players who value thermal protection for their racket.. Players who prioritise durability and resistance in their accessories.. Players seeking an elegant, discreet, and functional design.. Players who want to carry the essentials without the bulk of an oversized backpack or racket bag.. Conclusion: Versatility, durability, and organization for the modern player with the Multigame Tonal Black 2026 backpack. The Adidas Multigame Tonal Black 2026 backpack is an ideal option for those seeking a practical, durable backpack ready for daily use.. Thanks to its roll-top system, semi-rigid thermal compartment, reinforced base, and optimized organization, it allows you to carry all your equipment comfortably, safely, and efficiently.. If you want a backpack that combines durability, functionality, and minimalist design, the Adidas Multigame Tonal Black is the perfect ally on and off the court.",
