    "description": "Shoes Asics Gel-Resolution X Clay Blue FW26 - Maximum stability and absolute control to dominate from the baseline. The padel shoes Asics Gel Resolution X Clay Blue FW26 have been designed for demanding players looking for stability and comfort in every step during their most intense matches or training sessions.. This model has been specially developed with renewed comfort and stability for players who build their game from the baseline and need footwear capable of offering security during intense lateral movements, firmer landings and quick changes of direction without losing stability.. Among its cutting-edge technologies, the Gel technology in the forefoot area stands out to improve impact absorption during quick supports and aggressive landings, the FF BLAST technology, a lightweight and reactive foam to offer more comfortable and efficient cushioning, or technologies such as Dynawall or Dynalacing to improve fit and stability.. All this, together with a blue-colored design, provides a clean and fresh aesthetic combined with an elegant silhouette, making the Asics Gel-Resolution X Clay Blue FW26 the ideal shoes for players looking for great performance on the court without sacrificing comfort, stability and a modern and clean aesthetic.. Main Technical Features of the Asics Gel Resolution X Clay FW26 Shoes. The Asics Gel-Resolution X Clay stand out for integrating advanced technologies and high-quality materials aimed at improving stability, comfort and durability in high-intensity matches. Among them, the construction with a two-piece midsole that provides greater stability when supporting the foot or the outsole with a herringbone pattern and Aharplus and Pguard technologies to improve durability and reinforce the inner area stands out. Let’s take a closer look at their features:. Brand: ASICS. Model: Gel-Resolution X Clay. Season: FW26. Color: Blue. Sole type: Herringbone / Clay. Playing level: All levels. Playing style: Control / Baseline. Technologies and materials of the Asics Gel Resolution X Clay Blue FW26 padel shoes. DYNAWALL™: Superior stability during lateral movements. The DYNAWALL™ technology has been designed to improve stability during intense lateral movements and quick side-to-side transitions. In this new version, the DYNAWALL™ structure extends to the heel area, providing more solid and efficient support during aggressive supports and quick recoveries from the baseline.. DYNALACING™: Dynamic fit and greater foot support. The DYNALACING™ system of the Asics Gek-Resolution X Clay shoes allows for a more secure and stable fit during dynamic movements. Thanks to this technology, the foot remains better supported during accelerations, braking and sudden changes of direction, increasing the feeling of security and control during play.. FF BLAST™ PLUS ECO: Soft cushioning and prolonged comfort. The midsole incorporates the FF BLAST™ PLUS ECO technology, a lightweight and reactive foam developed to provide more comfortable and efficient cushioning. This compound helps absorb impacts better during intense movements, offering a softer stride and reducing fatigue during long matches.. GEL™ technology in the forefoot: Impact absorption and smoother transitions. The incorporation of the GEL™ technology in the forefoot area significantly improves impact absorption during quick supports and aggressive landings. This promotes smoother transitions and a greater feeling of comfort during explosive movements and constant displacements.. Two-piece midsole: Greater stability during landings. The Asics Gel-Resolution X Clay integrate a midsole with a two-piece design that improves stability during foot support. This construction promotes firmer and more balanced landings, especially useful for players who constantly cover both sides of the court.. AHARPLUS™ outsole and PGUARD™ reinforcement: Advanced resistance and durability. The clay outsole with herringbone pattern and AHARPLUS™ rubber has been designed to offer greater resistance to wear and long-lasting performance on clay court surfaces. In addition, the PGUARD™ technology reinforces the inner forefoot area, increasing protection against abrasion caused by dragging and aggressive movements during play.. Who are the Asics Gel-Resolution X Clay FW26 shoes for?. Baseline players looking for maximum stability during lateral movements.. Players who prioritize control and security during quick changes of direction.. Intensive players who need resistant and durable footwear for training and competition.. Players who value comfortable and stable cushioning during long matches.. Intermediate and advanced level players looking for a perfect balance between support, comfort and stability.. Conclusion: Control every point with stability and comfort with the Asics Gel-Resolution X Clay shoes. The Asics Gel-Resolution X Clay Blue FW26 shoes have been designed to offer solid and stable performance in the most demanding matches.. Thanks to technologies such as DYNAWALL™, DYNALACING™, the FF BLAST™ PLUS ECO cushioning and the GEL™ system, these shoes provide an exceptional combination of stability, impact absorption and security in every movement.. If you are looking for shoes capable of offering control, stability and maximum comfort to dominate from the baseline, the Asics Gel-Resolution X Clay FW26 are the choice you need.",
