    "description": "Adidas Protour Blue 2026 Racket Bag - Maximum organization, thermal protection and premium materials for demanding players. In today's padel, having well-organized and protected equipment is key to fully enjoying the game. The Adidas Protour Blue 2026 has been designed as an advanced solution for players seeking a high-level racket bag that combines capacity, practicality and excellent organization for their gear.. This model stands out for its optimized structure with two independent thermal compartments, one on each side, a spacious central area for equipment, and specific solutions to keep each item in perfect condition, such as its ventilated pocket for damp clothing. Regarding its aesthetics, the blue design with bronze details offers a modern and distinctive style both on and off the court.. Made with cutting-edge technical materials, this racket bag not only guarantees durability but also protection against moisture and weather conditions, making it an ideal choice for players who demand performance in every aspect of their equipment.. Technical Features of the Adidas Protour Blue 2026 Racket Bag. The Adidas Protour Blue 2026 has been developed to offer efficient space distribution, allowing transport of two rackets isolated from extreme temperatures thanks to its thermal compartments, clothing and large accessories in the main compartment, and damp clothing in the ventilated pocket. Let's see its full features:. Brand: Adidas. Model: Protour Blue. Season: 2026. Bag Type: Racket Bag. Color: Blue with bronze details. Capacity: Medium, with space for up to 2 rackets. Dimensions: 42 x 60 x 30 cm. Materials: 100% REC. PES 900D with TPU coating + 100% REC. PES 210D + raincover. Compartments: Main compartment for equipment, 2 lateral thermal compartments for rackets, ventilated pocket for damp clothing and top pocket with velvet lining. Design: Ergonomic structure with padded handles and comfortable carrying system. Technologies and Materials of the Adidas Protour Blue 2026 Racket Bag. Technical Fabric REC. PES 900D with TPU Coating: Maximum durability and protection. This racket bag is made with high-density recycled polyester (REC. PES 900D), a material especially resistant to wear, abrasion and intensive use. Additionally, it incorporates a TPU coating that acts as a protective barrier against moisture, splashes and adverse weather conditions.. The use of REC. PES 210D inside keeps it lightweight without compromising strength, while the raincover adds an extra layer of protection in rainy or highly humid situations.. Double Thermal Compartment: Protection for your rackets. The Adidas Protour Blue features two independent thermal compartments, located on both sides of the racket bag, designed to protect rackets from temperature changes. Each compartment can store one racket, ensuring balanced distribution and optimal protection.. This system helps preserve the properties of the rackets' materials, preventing heat or cold from affecting their performance and extending their lifespan.. Main compartment and optimized organization. The central compartment offers ample space to carry clothing, towels and accessories, allowing everything to be kept organized and accessible. Its design facilitates efficient equipment distribution, ideal for players seeking practicality in their daily routine.. Ventilated pocket: separation of damp clothing. The racket bag includes an independent ventilated pocket designed for damp or used clothing, preventing moisture buildup and bad odors in the rest of the equipment. This solution improves hygiene and organization after intense training sessions or matches by not mixing clean clothes with post-match wear.. Top pocket with velvet lining: protection for personal items. At the top, it includes a pocket with velvet lining, designed to protect delicate items such as mobile phones, glasses or personal accessories. This detail adds extra care and reinforces the premium character of the product.. Ergonomic carrying system. The Adidas Protour Blue design incorporates padded handles and an ergonomic structure that allow comfortable and balanced transport of the racket bag. The weight distribution with backpack-style straps facilitates movement, even when the bag is fully loaded.. Who is the Adidas Protour Blue 2026 Racket Bag for?. This Adidas racket bag is intended for:. Demanding players looking for a racket bag with technical materials and high durability.. Regular players who need to transport their equipment in an organized manner.. Players who value protection for their rackets through thermal compartments.. Players who prioritize modern design combined with advanced functionality.. Conclusion: Organization, protection and premium design in one racket bag with the Adidas Protour 2026. The Adidas Protour Blue 2026 represents the perfect balance between technology, capacity and design tailored for the modern player.. Thanks to its high-resistance materials, independent thermal compartments, optimized organization and specific solutions for clothing and personal items, this racket bag guarantees a complete experience on and off the court.. If you are looking for a racket bag that combines protection, durability and style, the Adidas Protour Blue 2026 is an ideal option to take your equipment to the next level.",
