    "sourceProductId": "42722756597",
    "sourceCategory": "Tennis",
    "description": "Head Coello Tour Padel Bag 2025 - Padel Racket Bag for players who value organization and great capacity backed by Coello. In the world of padel, having the right equipment is essential to maximize performance and comfort during every training session or competition. The Head Coello Tour Padel Bag 2025 presents itself as a comprehensive solution for the most demanding players looking for a racket bag that combines advanced functionality, remarkable capacity, and a modern, attractive design.. Made to meet the demands of athletes, this racket bag stands out for its versatility and for incorporating exclusive technologies that guarantee optimal protection and organization of your equipment, such as the CCT+ technology to keep your rackets isolated from temperature changes, the integrated footwear compartment, and additional pockets for accessories.. The Coello Tour Padel Bag edition in black with red details not only offers an elegant and contemporary style, but also incorporates state-of-the-art fabrics, a red interior reflecting the player's style, and an ergonomic transport system that facilitates carrying without sacrificing comfort. This racket bag is designed to accompany you in every match and training session, ensuring all your equipment is protected and organized for easy and quick access at all times.. Technical Features of the Head Coello Tour Padel Bag 2025. This Head Coello Tour Padel Bag 2025 stands out for its large capacity, allowing you to carry up to 7 rackets thanks to its 3 compartments, one of which features CCT+ protection (Climate Control Plus) to protect rackets from extreme temperatures and temperature changes. Additionally, it features an integrated footwear compartment so you can keep your clothing separate from your shoes to avoid unwanted stains. Let's look at its features in detail:. Brand: Head. Model: Coello Tour Padel Bag. Season: 2025. Bag Type: Racket Bag. Color: Black with red details and red interior. Capacity: 40 L with space for up to 7 rackets. Dimensions: 60 X 28.5 X 36.5 cm. Materials: 80% Polyester, 20% PU. Compartments: 3 main compartments, one with CCT+ technology, integrated footwear compartment, and a total of 4 accessory pockets—three external and one internal.. Design: Padded top handles, ergonomic backpack-style design, red interior, and red Coello crown logos distributed across the racket bag. Technologies and Materials of the Head Coello Tour 2025 Racket Bag. Exclusive Arturo Coello Design with Red Details and Crown Logo. One of the most outstanding features of the Head Coello Tour Padel Bag 2025 is its exclusive design developed in collaboration with professional player Arturo Coello. Its exterior finish in black with red details, the red interior, and the integration of the Coello crown logo in red at various points on the racket bag provide a unique, modern, and easily recognizable aesthetic both on and off the court.. High-Resistance Fabrics: Polyester and Polyurethane. This Head Coello Tour Padel Bag is made from a blend of 80% polyester and 20% polyurethane (PU) that ensures optimal resistance against wear, abrasion, and exposure to weather conditions. Polyester provides durability and lightness, while polyurethane offers partial waterproofing and greater protection against moisture and stains.. CCT+ Technology (Climate Control Temperature Plus). The CCT+ technology is one of the standout features in this Head racket bag, focused on advanced equipment protection. This technology consists of thermal insulation and temperature regulation designed to protect padel rackets from sudden temperature changes that can negatively affect their performance and durability.. The CCT+ compartment helps keep rackets in optimal condition, preventing their materials from being affected by excessive heat or intense cold. This technology is found only in one of the main compartments, so you can carry your favorite rackets more protected.. Highly Functional Compartments and Pockets. The Head Coello Tour Padel Bag 2025 is equipped with three main compartments that allow carrying up to seven rackets, an ideal capacity for players who use different models or want to have spare rackets on hand.. Additionally, it features two large external zippered pockets for storing accessories like grips, balls, or other essentials, an external pocket specially designed for a mobile phone for quick and secure access, and a final internal zippered pocket for other accessories or personal items you want to keep more secure.. Integrated Footwear Compartment. The inclusion of a separate compartment for shoes is a feature that shows attention to detail and understanding of the player's needs. This separate space prevents dirt from shoes and odors mixing with the rest of the equipment, maintaining proper hygiene and reinforcing the great capacity and functionality with which this racket bag has been designed.. Ergonomic Backpack-Style Transport System. To facilitate carrying the racket bag, Head has integrated a backpack-style strap system that distributes weight evenly across the shoulders and back. These padded and adjustable straps adapt to different body types and carrying preferences. This ergonomic solution reduces fatigue during transport and improves mobility.. Environmental Commitment: Recycled Materials and Sustainable Labeling. Beyond functionality, Head demonstrates a strong commitment to sustainability. The bag's hang tag is made from recycled paper and attached with a hemp cord, and the protective cover in which the bag is delivered is made of recycled plastic, reinforcing the brand's ecological commitment.. Who is the Head Coello Tour Padel Bag 2025 for?. This Head Coello Tour Padel Bag is designed for:. Players who require spacious and organized storage for their equipment.. High-level players who need to carry several rackets to play with different styles or simply have spare rackets.. Advanced players who understand the importance of protecting their rackets from temperature changes and value technologies like CCT+.. Players seeking a modern and elegant design with an exclusive identity inspired by Arturo Coello and who appreciate a racket bag with a distinctive look on the court.. Players who prioritize organization for their equipment and value racket bags that include a specific footwear compartment, accessory pockets, and separate compartments for rackets.. Fans of Arturo Coello who want to have the same equipment or reflect his style on the court.. Conclusion: Enjoy the complete padel experience with a high-capacity racket bag to carry everything you need with the Head Coello Tour Padel Bag. The Head Coello Tour Padel Bag 2025 represents the perfect synthesis of technological innovation, capacity, and design aimed at maximum performance and comfort for the padel player.. Thanks to its high-quality materials, CCT+ climate control system, and intelligent compartment distribution, this racket bag ensures every sports item stays protected and organized, facilitating daily training and competition logistics.. This Coello Tour Padel Bag is an outstanding choice for those who value quality, advanced functionality, and sustainable commitment in their sports products. Whether you are an amateur player who trains occasionally or a competitor demanding the best for your equipment, this racket bag is designed to exceed your expectations. Don’t miss this opportunity and get the Head Coello Tour Padel Bag 2025 to elevate your total padel experience and enjoy maximum comfort and protection for your equipment!",
