    "sourceCategory": "Tennis",
    "description": "Asics GEL-RESOLUTION X Clay White/Green SS26 Shoes - Maximum stability and absolute control to dominate from the baseline. The Asics GEL-RESOLUTION X Clay White/Green SS26 have been developed for players seeking the perfect combination of stability, cushioning, and structural support during the most demanding matches.. This model is specially designed for players who build their game from the baseline and need footwear capable of providing security in intense lateral movements, firmer landings, and quick changes of direction without losing stability.. The white design with green details offers a clean, modern, and sporty aesthetic, combining elegance with a dynamic and fresh touch that stands out on the court.. Technical Features of the Asics GEL-RESOLUTION X Clay SS26. The Asics GEL-RESOLUTION X Clay stand out by integrating advanced technologies aimed at improving stability, comfort, and durability in high-intensity matches on clay courts.. Brand: Asics. Model: GEL-RESOLUTION X Clay. Season: SS26. Color: White with green and purple details. Sole type: Espiga / Clay. Playing level: All levels. Playing style: Control / Baseline. Technologies and materials of the Asics GEL-RESOLUTION X Clay White/Green SS26 shoes. DYNAWALL™: Superior stability in lateral movements. The DYNAWALL™ technology is designed to enhance stability in intense lateral movements and quick side-to-side shifts. In this new version, the DYNAWALL™ structure extends to the heel area, providing stronger and more efficient support during aggressive landings and fast recoveries from the baseline.. DYNALACING™: Dynamic fit and greater foot support. The DYNALACING™ system of the Asics GEL-Resolution X Clay shoes allows for a more secure and stable fit during dynamic movements. Thanks to this technology, the foot remains better held during accelerations, stops, and sudden changes of direction, increasing the feeling of security and control during play.. FF BLAST™ PLUS ECO: Soft cushioning and prolonged comfort. The midsole incorporates FF BLAST™ PLUS ECO technology, a lightweight and responsive foam developed to provide more comfortable and efficient cushioning. This compound helps better absorb impacts during intense movements, offering a softer step and reducing fatigue in long matches.. GEL™ technology in the forefoot: Impact absorption and smoother transitions. The inclusion of GEL™ technology in the forefoot area significantly improves impact absorption during quick landings and aggressive footfalls. This promotes smoother transitions and a greater sense of comfort during explosive movements and constant shifts.. Two-piece midsole: Greater stability on landings. The Asics GEL-RESOLUTION X Clay feature a two-piece midsole design that enhances stability during foot support. This construction promotes firmer and more balanced landings, especially useful for players who constantly cover both sides of the court.. AHARPLUS™ sole and PGUARD™ reinforcement: Advanced resistance and durability. The AHARPLUS™ rubber sole is designed to offer greater wear resistance and long-lasting performance on clay surfaces. Additionally, the PGUARD™ technology reinforces the inner forefoot area, increasing protection against abrasion caused by dragging and aggressive movements during play.. More sustainable manufacturing: Lower environmental impact. The insole of the Asics GEL-RESOLUTION X Clay is manufactured through a solution-dyeing process that significantly reduces water consumption and carbon emissions compared to conventional methods. This process allows for more responsible production while maintaining the footwear's performance and quality intact.. Who are the Asics GEL-RESOLUTION X Clay SS26 shoes for?. Baseline players seeking maximum stability in lateral movements.. Players who prioritize control and security in quick changes of direction.. Intensive players who need durable and resistant footwear for training and competition.. Players who value comfortable and stable cushioning during long matches.. Intermediate and advanced level players looking for the perfect balance between support, comfort, and stability.. Conclusion: Control every point with stability and comfort with the Asics GEL-RESOLUTION X Clay shoes. The Asics GEL-RESOLUTION X Clay White/Green SS26 have been designed to offer solid and stable performance in the most demanding matches.. Thanks to technologies such as DYNAWALL™, DYNALACING™, FF BLAST™ PLUS ECO cushioning, and the GEL™ system, these shoes provide an exceptional combination of stability, impact absorption, and security in every movement.. If you are looking for shoes capable of offering control, durability, lateral support, and maximum comfort to dominate from the baseline, the Asics GEL-RESOLUTION X Clay SS26 are a perfect choice to elevate your level of play.",
