    "sourceCategory": "Tennis",
    "description": "Adidas Cross IT Light 3.4 2025 Racket - Martita Ortega's racket for demanding women seeking control, speed, and precision. The Adidas Cross IT Light 3.4 2025 Marta Ortega has been designed for women looking for a lightweight, manageable, and precise racket capable of offering maximum control without sacrificing balanced power in decisive moments.. Chosen by professional player Marta Ortega, this racket stands out for its combination of maneuverability, comfort, and reaction speed, becoming an excellent option for intermediate and advanced women who enjoy building points with intelligence and precision.. Thanks to its round shape, medium balance, and incorporation of advanced technologies such as Dynamic Air Flow, Spin Blade Mold, and 24K aluminized carbon, this racket offers a balanced and versatile playing experience both in defense and attack.. Technical Features of the Adidas Cross IT Light 3.4 2025 Marta Ortega Racket. The Adidas Cross IT Light 3.4 2025 has been developed for women who prioritize control, execution speed, and versatility during play.. Brand: Adidas. Model: Cross IT Light 3.4. Player: Marta Ortega. Year: 2025. Shape: Round. Balance: Medium. Weight System: 345-360 gr. Core: EVA Soft Energy. Faces: 24K Aluminized Carbon. Surface: Rough. Playing level: Intermediate / Advanced. Playing style: Control / Versatile. Technologies and Materials of the Adidas Cross IT Light 3.4 2025 Racket by Martita Ortega. 24K Aluminized Carbon: Greater stiffness and ball output. The faces of the Adidas Cross IT Light 3.4 2025 are made with 24K aluminized carbon, a high-performance material that provides an excellent combination of stiffness, durability, and responsiveness. This carbon allows energy from the hit to be transmitted more efficiently, offering great precision in offensive shots and excellent stability on intense impacts.. The aluminized finish adds extra durability to the racket, enabling it to maintain its properties and performance for much longer.. EVA Soft Energy Rubber: Comfort and control in every shot. The EVA Soft Energy rubber core offers a comfortable feel and great vibration absorption, promoting a more comfortable game and reducing fatigue during long matches. Thanks to its softer density, this rubber improves ball output and provides excellent control in defensive shots and situations where precision is key.. Round shape and medium balance: Maximum maneuverability and control. The combination of a round shape and medium balance results in an extremely manageable and balanced racket. The centered sweet spot facilitates more consistent shots even on off-center hits, helping maintain control and stability throughout the match. Its round shape favors control and defensive play, creating the ideal balance between control and the power needed for attacks.. Dynamic Air Flow: Optimized aerodynamics for greater speed. The Dynamic Air Flow technology incorporates an aerodynamic design in the heart of the racket that improves airflow during movement. This reduces swing resistance and allows the racket to accelerate more easily, enabling faster shots and better reaction capacity in intense rallies.. Extra Power Grip: More power with less effort. The Adidas Cross IT Light 3.4 features a longer grip thanks to the Extra Power Grip technology. This construction with a longer handle than other rackets on the market improves racket inertia and helps generate greater power on certain shots without increasing arm effort, meaning it helps generate power more easily.. 11 Thirteen System: Greater stiffness and consistency. The 11 Thirteen technology in the Cross IT Light 3.4 consists of combining eleven smaller diameter central holes with others of standard size to improve the racket's structural stiffness. This system provides a more solid hitting sensation, improves durability, and promotes a more stable and consistent response on every impact.. Spin Blade Mold: More spin and control on the ball. The surface incorporates the Spin Blade Mold technology, a rough relief designed to increase friction with the ball during impact. Thanks to this texture, you will achieve shots with spin such as topspin or slice more easily, increasing tactical control, complicating the opponent's return, and adding a tactical advantage on the court.. Who is the Adidas Cross IT Light 3.4 by Martita Ortega for?. Intermediate and advanced women seeking a balanced and manageable racket.. Women who prioritize control and precision during play.. Women looking for a racket that allows them to alternate between defense and attack during changes of pace in the game.. Players seeking a lightweight racket to improve maneuverability and speed on the court.. Fans of Marta Ortega who want to compete with her official racket or equip themselves with a racket that conveys her personality and style.. Women who base their strategy on defensive and control play to dominate the opponent and win points.. Frequently Asked Questions about the Cross IT Light 3.4 2025 Racket. What type of player benefits most from this racket?. The Adidas Cross IT Light 3.4 2025 is especially recommended for women seeking control, comfort, and reaction speed without losing offensive capability.. What advantages does the lightweight provide?. The reduced weight improves racket movement speed, facilitates defensive reaction, and reduces muscle fatigue during long matches or intense training sessions.. Conclusion: The ideal racket for women seeking control, speed, and versatility. The Adidas Cross IT Light 3.4 2025 Marta Ortega combines lightness, precision, and advanced technologies to offer balanced performance in all phases of the game.. Thanks to materials such as 24K aluminized carbon, EVA Soft Energy rubber, and technologies like Dynamic Air Flow, Spin Blade Mold, and the 11 Thirteen system, this racket provides an excellent combination of control, maneuverability, and offensive capacity.. If you are looking for a comfortable, reactive, and defensive racket to dominate every point with intelligence and precision, without losing the necessary power when the opportunity arises, the Adidas Cross IT Light 3.4 2025 is one of the most complete options to elevate your level on the court.",
