    "source": "padel-market",
    "sourceProductId": "43311667588",
    "sourceCategory": "Tennis",
    "description": "Asics GEL DEDICATE 8 Padel White W SS26 Shoes - Stability and dynamic design for women seeking confidence in every move. The Asics GEL DEDICATE 8 Padel White W SS26 have been specifically developed for women looking for comfortable, stable, and flexible shoes to move with full confidence on the court. This model stands out especially for offering great stability in lateral movements and changes of direction, without losing comfort or freedom of movement during play.. Thanks to its reinforced structure, integration of technologies aimed at improving stability, and GEL cushioning, these shoes provide a much more comfortable and secure experience both in training and intense matches.. They feature a white design combined with purple and pink details that provide a clean and dynamic aesthetic, positioning them as one of the best shoes for beginner and intermediate level players who want reliable, comfortable, and stable footwear to continue progressing in padel.. Technical Features of the Asics GEL DEDICATE 8 Padel White W SS26 Shoes. The Asics GEL DEDICATE 8 Padel stand out for their stability and cushioning thanks to technologies such as Trusstic and the synthetic leather wrap upper. Additionally, their reinforced construction combined with a lightweight and flexible structure allows for safer and more natural movements on the court.. Brand: Asics. Model: Gel Dedicate 8 Padel W. Season: SS26. Color: White with purple and pink details. Sole type: Espiga / Clay. Playing level: Beginner / Intermediate. Technologies and Materials of the Asics GEL DEDICATE 8 Padel White W SS26. GEL Technology: Soft cushioning and excellent impact absorption. The Asics GEL DEDICATE 8 Padel W incorporate the renowned GEL technology in the midsole, designed to improve impact absorption and provide a softer, more comfortable feel during play.. Thanks to this cushioning, the shoes help reduce pressure on joints during repetitive supports and intense movements, promoting greater comfort in both training sessions and long matches.. TRUSSTIC™ and wrap sole: Greater stability and control in movements. The TRUSSTIC™ technology along with the wrap sole structure have been developed to enhance stability and provide a more secure feel during quick changes of direction and lateral movements.. This technology helps keep the foot firmer during play and facilitates smoother, more controlled transitions, especially in aggressive side-to-side movements.. Upper with synthetic leather overlays: Firm support and increased durability. The upper features synthetic leather overlays designed to increase support and improve the footwear's resistance to wear. Thanks to this synthetic leather overlay, the shoes provide a greater sense of stability and security during intense supports, helping to keep the foot properly held during quick movements and changes of pace.. Durable toe reinforcements: Extra protection against wear. The Asics GEL DEDICATE 8 Padel W include highly durable synthetic leather reinforcements on the toe to improve durability against continuous friction with the court. This additional protection helps extend the shoes' lifespan and provides greater security during aggressive movements and intense stops.. Flexible and lightweight design: Freedom of movement during play. Another standout feature of this model is its lightweight and flexible construction, designed to promote more natural and fluid movements on the court.. Who are the Asics GEL DEDICATE 8 Padel White W SS26 for?. Beginner and intermediate women players seeking stability and comfort on the court.. Players who perform frequent lateral movements and need good support.. Women starting in the sport looking for durable and reliable shoes for training and matches.. Players who want a fresh and dynamic aesthetic on the court.. Conclusion: Stability, comfort, and security with the Asics GEL DEDICATE 8 Padel White W SS26. The Asics GEL DEDICATE 8 Padel White W SS26 have been developed to offer a comfortable, stable, and secure experience on the court, becoming an excellent option for women players who want to continue evolving their game with confidence.. Thanks to technologies like GEL, TRUSSTIC™, synthetic leather reinforcements, and their flexible structure, these shoes provide stability and cushioning without losing freedom of movement during every step.. If you are a player looking for shoes that combine comfort, stability, and a clean, dynamic aesthetic, the Asics GEL DEDICATE 8 Padel White W SS26 are an excellent choice to enjoy padel with total security and comfort and continue advancing in your professional journey.",
