    "description": "Pack of 2 HEAD Base Backpack 17L Black/Yellow. Discover the set of two HEAD Base Backpack 17L in Black/Yellow, perfect for sports enthusiasts and padel players who value both functionality and style.. Main Features. Optimal capacity: Each backpack has a 17-liter volume, offering enough space to carry all your essentials effortlessly.. Dimensions: Measuring 54 x 33 x 13 cm, they provide the perfect storage solution for your sports equipment.. Durable material: Made from 100% polyester, ensuring durability and lightweight comfort.. Functional compartments: Includes a dedicated compartment for one or two rackets, a spacious main compartment, a front zippered pocket for small items, and two side mesh pockets ideal for water bottles or padel balls.. Comfortable carrying: Equipped with padded, adjustable shoulder straps and an additional hand strap for versatile carrying options.. Modern design: The combination of black with neon yellow accents adds a vibrant and contemporary touch.. Benefits of the Set. This pack of two backpacks is ideal for padel partners, teams, or anyone looking for an extra bag. It provides excellent value for money, ensuring you always have a reliable and stylish backpack for training and matches.. Versatility and Style. Beyond padel, these backpacks are suitable for various sports and even daily use, thanks to their practical and sleek design.. Equip yourself with the HEAD Base Backpack 17L Black/Yellow twin pack and enjoy the perfect balance of practicality and style for your sports activities.",
