    "sourceProductId": "43643575398",
    "sourceCategory": "Tennis",
    "description": "Asics GEL DEDICATE 8 Padel Black/Green SS26 Shoes - Exceptional stability to dominate every movement on the court. The Asics Gel Dedicate 8 Padel Black/Green SS26 have been designed for players seeking shoes that provide great stability in every movement without sacrificing comfort and freedom of movement. This model is especially characterized by offering a firm and secure footing in lateral movements and changes of direction, helping to maintain control and confidence in every point.. Thanks to its reinforced structure, the integration of stability-oriented technologies, and GEL cushioning, these shoes provide a comfortable and smooth experience both in training and your first matches.. Additionally, its black design combined with green details offers a dynamic, modern, and energetic aesthetic, ideal for players looking for performance and style on the court. Above all, recommended for beginner and intermediate level players who want reliable, comfortable, and stable shoes to keep improving.. Technical Features of the Asics GEL DEDICATE 8 Padel Black/Green SS26 Shoes. The Asics GEL DEDICATE 8 Padel incorporate specific technologies designed to enhance stability, cushioning, and flexibility during play. Their reinforced construction combined with a lightweight and flexible structure allows for safer and more natural movements on the court.. Brand: Asics. Model: Gel Dedicate 8 Padel. Season: SS26. Colour: Black with green details. Sole type: Espiga / Clay. Playing level: Beginner / Intermediate. Technologies and Materials of the Asics GEL DEDICATE 8 Padel Black/Green SS26. GEL Technology: Soft cushioning and excellent impact absorption. The Asics Gel Dedicate 8 Padel feature the renowned GEL technology in the midsole, designed to improve impact absorption and provide a softer, more comfortable feel during play.. Thanks to this cushioning, the shoes help reduce pressure on joints during repetitive supports and intense movements, promoting greater comfort in both training and long matches.. TRUSSTIC™ and wrap-around sole: Greater stability and control in movements. The TRUSSTIC™ technology along with the wrap-around sole structure have been developed to improve stability and provide a more secure feel during quick changes of direction and lateral movements.. This technology helps keep the foot firmer during play and supports smoother, more controlled transitions, especially in aggressive side-to-side movements.. Upper with synthetic leather overlays: Firm support and increased durability. The upper incorporates synthetic leather overlays designed to increase support and improve the footwear's resistance to wear. Thanks to this synthetic leather overlay, the shoes provide a greater sense of stability and security during intense supports, helping to keep the foot properly held during fast movements and changes of pace.. Durable toe reinforcements: Extra protection against wear. The Asics Gel Dedicate 8 Padel include highly durable synthetic leather reinforcements on the toe to enhance durability against continuous friction with the court. This additional protection helps extend the lifespan of the shoes and provides greater security during aggressive movements and intense stops.. Flexible and lightweight design: Freedom of movement during play. Another standout feature of this model is its lightweight and flexible construction, designed to promote more natural and fluid movements on the court.. Who are the Asics GEL DEDICATE 8 Padel Black/Green SS26 for?. Beginner and intermediate men looking for stability and comfort on court.. Players who perform frequent lateral movements and need good support.. Athletes who prioritize comfortable cushioning and a softer step.. Players starting in the sport who want durable and reliable shoes for training and matches.. Players who desire a dynamic, modern, and sporty aesthetic on court.. Conclusion: Stability, comfort, and security with the Asics Gel Dedicate 8 Padel Black/Green SS26. The Asics Gel Dedicate 8 Padel Black/Green SS26 have been developed to offer a comfortable, stable, and secure experience on court, becoming an excellent option for players who want to keep evolving their game with confidence.. Thanks to technologies like GEL, TRUSSTIC™, synthetic leather reinforcements, and their flexible structure, these shoes provide stability and cushioning without losing freedom of movement in every step.. If you are looking for shoes that combine comfort, stability, and a dynamic, sporty aesthetic, the Asics Gel Dedicate 8 Padel Black/Green SS26 are an excellent choice to enjoy padel with total security and comfort.",
