    "source": "padel-market",
    "sourceProductId": "43467043827",
    "sourceCategory": "Tennis",
    "description": "Asics Gel Challenger 14 Clay Blue W SS24 Shoes - Comfort and firmness to dominate points from the back of the court with great comfort. The Asics Gel-Challenger 14 Clay Blue W SS24 have been designed for women players seeking comfortable, stable, and reliable shoes to control from the back of the court. This model stands out especially for offering an excellent combination of cushioning and support, making it a great choice for players who prioritize control and comfort at the baseline.. This Gel-Challenger 14 Clay model features a lighter and more agile structure, providing a more dynamic and free feeling without losing firmness and stability during aggressive footwork and direction changes. Additionally, it sports a blue color design combined with light blue and fluorescent green details, giving it a modern, sporty, and very energetic look.. Technical Features of the Asics Gel Challenger 14 Clay Blue W SS24 Shoes. The Asics Gel Challenger 14 Clay W incorporate specific technologies developed to improve stability, comfort, and durability during play. Thanks to their lightweight structure and construction aimed at baseline players, they offer an excellent sense of security and control in lateral movements and quick transitions.. Brand: Asics. Model: Gel Challenger 14 Clay W. Season: SS24. Color: Blue with light blue and fluorescent green details. Sole type: Espiga / Clay. Playing level: Intermediate / Advanced. Technologies and Materials of the Asics Gel Challenger 14 Clay Blue W SS24. GEL™ Technology: Comfortable cushioning and impact absorption. The Asics Gel Challenger 14 Clay W feature the renowned GEL™ technology in the rear midsole area, designed to improve impact absorption and provide a much more comfortable step during play. Thanks to this cushioning, the shoes help reduce pressure on joints during repetitive movements and aggressive footwork, promoting a greater comfort sensation during long training sessions and matches.. Wingwall™: Greater lateral stability in intense movements. The Wingwall™ technology includes a stabilizing piece located on the outer lateral side designed to enhance stability and increase security during quick direction changes. Thanks to Wingwall™, the shoes offer a firmer feeling in lateral movements and aggressive stops, helping maintain control during high-intensity points from the back of the court.. Reinforced upper and padded collar: More comfortable and secure fit. The upper incorporates reinforced synthetic materials that improve the footwear's structural stability and help keep the foot properly secured during play. Additionally, the padded collar provides a much more comfortable and enveloping sensation around the ankle, improving fit and increasing the feeling of security during fast movements.. Clay sole with espiga pattern: Traction and stability in every movement. The espiga sole has been designed to offer excellent traction on clay courts and sand-based padel courts, allowing much safer and more controlled movements.. Moreover, the design with separated grooves and a wider support surface helps improve stability and promotes softer, more comfortable landings during play.. Ortholite™ Insole: Greater comfort and moisture control. The Asics Gel Challenger 14 Clay W include an Ortholite™ insole designed to enhance comfort and promote better moisture management inside the shoes. Thanks to Ortholite™, the foot stays cooler and drier during play, increasing comfort even in long matches or intense training sessions.. PGUARD™ and AHARPLUS™: Greater resistance and durability. The PGUARD™ technology reinforces the most wear-prone areas to increase resistance against abrasion and frequent dragging on the court. On the other hand, the AHARPLUS™ compound located in strategic sole areas significantly improves durability against abrasion, helping maintain the shoes' performance for much longer.. Lightweight and agile structure: Greater speed and freedom of movement. Another standout feature of this Gel-Challenger 14 generation is its lighter and less bulky construction, allowing a much more agile and dynamic feeling during play. This structure favors quick movements and smoother transitions, ideal for players who want to cover the court more easily without feeling excessively weighed down by their footwear.. Who are the Asics Gel Challenger 14 Clay Blue W SS24 for?. Intermediate and advanced players seeking stability and comfort on court.. Baseline players who perform constant lateral movements.. Athletes who prioritize a firm step and good cushioning.. Players looking for durable and reliable shoes for frequent training and matches.. Players who want a modern, energetic, and sporty aesthetic on court.. Conclusion: Stability, comfort, and dynamism with the Asics Gel Challenger 14 Clay Blue W SS24. The Asics Gel Challenger 14 Clay Blue W SS24 have been developed to offer a stable, comfortable, and dynamic experience on court, becoming an excellent option for players seeking security and comfort in every movement.. Thanks to technologies like GEL™, Wingwall™, Ortholite™, PGUARD™, and AHARPLUS™, these shoes provide stability, cushioning, and a great sense of confidence during play.. If you are looking for shoes that combine comfort, stability, lightness, and a modern, energetic aesthetic, the Asics Gel Challenger 14 Clay Blue W SS24 are an excellent choice to dominate every point from the back of the court.",
